# Context7 Documentation Rule

Always use Context7 MCP when I need library/API documentation, code generation, setup or configuration steps without me having to explicitly ask.

## Usage
- **Specific Library:** If you know the library, append `use context7` or specify the library ID (e.g., `/supabase/supabase`).
- **Specific Version:** Mention the version in your prompt (e.g., "Next.js 14 middleware use context7").

## Examples
- "How do I set up authentication with Supabase? use context7"
- "Show me the docs for Pinecone vector search use context7"
